2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of generative adversarial networks to generate synthetic patient records is an application of artificial intelligence.

5. cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper discusses privacy concerns and the potential risks associated with sharing real patient data. This falls under the domain of computers and society.
